fell through.

22:39.728 --> 22:41.499
‐Oh...
‐And then, with the weather

22:41.532 --> 22:43.402
that we've been having...

22:43.435 --> 22:44.838
I mean, I really,

22:44.872 --> 22:46.776
really need to get
to the airport early, okay?

22:46.809 --> 22:48.078
COLIN:
Bye, Gail.

22:48.111 --> 22:50.049
‐Ciao. Bye, guys.
‐We love you. I like her.

22:50.082 --> 22:52.420
‐COLIN: Bye, Gail.
‐(growling)

22:52.453 --> 22:53.656
‐Oh!
‐Whoa.

22:53.690 --> 22:55.459
NANDOR:
Careful of the fence!

22:55.493 --> 22:57.698
‐(groans, growls)
‐Ah...

22:57.731 --> 22:59.133
ANTON:
Bye, sweet Gail!

22:59.167 --> 23:01.071
NANDOR:
Farewell, my Gail.

